These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, brown, amber, azure
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy, balloon-flower, marigold
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who likes grey is the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Color    | brown  | azure | amber    | grey       |
| Flower         | daisy | marigold    | balloon-flower      | aconite |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
House: futuristic, ranch-style, farmhouse, modern
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, chess, snooker
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person driving the roller is the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| House        | farmhouse   | ranch-style | futuristic     | modern      |
| Game         | go | chess | snooker | scrabble |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, amaryllis, daffodil, tulip
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the person drinking juice is the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | juice | soy-milk | tea | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Flower   | iris | daffodil    | tulip | amaryllis    |

