.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, red, aquamarine, lavender
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, coffee, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the person who likes aquamarine is the person driving the train##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person who likes red is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Color         | blood-red | lavender | aquamarine | red |
| Beverage       | tea     | iced-tea      | almond-milk     | coffee      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

