.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, firefighter, lawyer, dancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, horror, thriller, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, blood-red, purple, lilac
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the lawyer is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person who likes green is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the social-worker is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
6. the social-worker is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the dancer is the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Job         | lawyer   | dancer | firefighter  | social-worker      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | epic        | western  | horror       |
| Color         | green | purple    | blood-red | lilac |

