.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, cricket, rugby, biathlon
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, artichoke, lettuce, garlic
1. the accountant is the person eating artichoke##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the writer##1
4. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is the mechanic##1
7. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
8. the writer is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Sport   | biathlon   | rugby  | cricket | swimming   |
| Food   | garlic   | cucumber     | lettuce | artichoke       |

