.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
House: farmhouse, tower, gothic-revival, wooden
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, skydiving, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, vegafina, bongani, old-henry
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
2. the tower house is on the far right##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| House          | farmhouse  | wooden | gothic-revival   | tower     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking   | baking  | skydiving |
| Cigar   | bongani         | bluemaster  | vegafina | old-henry  |

