.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, juice, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, july, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller, bike, quad-bike
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person drinking juice##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | juice     | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Birthday   | april  | january | july       | june    |
| Transport   | roller   | quad-bike | snowmobile    | bike |

