.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, onion, pepper, tomato
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, ferret, mouse
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, superhero, documentary, family
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is the person eating onion##1
5. the person eating onion is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | pepper        | tomato   | onion  | cucumber   |
| Pet   | bird         | mouse     | hedgehog    | ferret       |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero | sports | documentary | family |

