.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, pall-mall, alhambra, ritmeester
City: prague, marseilles, nizza, hamburg
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the ritmeester-smoker is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | pall-mall    | alhambra | ritmeester | dannemann        |
| City       | hamburg | prague  | marseilles | nizza     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

