.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, romance, spy, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, pop, dubstep, reggae
1. the fan of ambient is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is the fan of dubstep##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Movie-Genre         | fantasy  | western | romance  | spy |
| Sport       | volleyball | rugby        | weightlifting | cricket       |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | pop          | reggae          | dubstep       |

