4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| City         | venice | miami    | hamburg        | liverpool |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
