.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, peas, apricot, pomegranate
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, pakistani, russian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, 7up, iced-tea
1. the person eating onion is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the russian##1
3. the canadian is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating onion##1
7. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
8. the indonesian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Food   | peas   | pomegranate  | onion    | apricot    |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | canadian  | indonesian |
| Beverage     | iced-tea  | sprite | 7up | soy-milk        |

