.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
House: cape-cod, colonial, victorian, art-deco
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, camping, filmmaking, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, handball, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the victorian house##1
2. the victorian house is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the art-deco house##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the cape-cod house is the person who's hobby is chess##1
8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| House      | cape-cod        | art-deco    | colonial | victorian      |
| Hobby   | chess        | sudoku   | camping  | filmmaking  |
| Sport         | weightlifting | handball | soccer   | climbing |

