3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the owner of the horse##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby          | sudoku     | collecting   | cooking | rock-climbing |
| Birthday   | october | january | august | june   |
| Pet           | rabbit    | fish     | bird      | horse     |

