There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, hot-chocolate, cola, fanta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, parkour, tennis
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking sprite is the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
7. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Cigar           | swisher  | baccarat  | pall-mall | fonseca |
| Beverage   | fanta   | sprite | hot-chocolate   | cola      |
| Sport         | badminton | parkour    | biathlon   | tennis         |

 